/**
 * Contract Test: Digest Generator Schedule Management
 * T015 - MUST FAIL before implementation
 *
 * This test validates the digest schedule management endpoints according to the OpenAPI contract.
 * The endpoints must handle digest scheduling configuration including category-specific timing,
 * delivery preferences, and template assignments.
